{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/Hallpass/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Sebastian Klingler | UI Engineer","author":"Sebastian Klingler"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"d4e70f46-b667-5f1f-9a04-f630cdaed7ca","html":"<p><a href=\"http://www.hallpass.io/\">Hallpass</a> is a password manager focused on security via biometrics. It allows users to sign in to websites on any device by using the fingerprint sensor on their phone.</p>\n<p>Hallpass was conceived of at <a href=\"https://www.hackdfw.com/\">Hack-DFW</a> 2016 as a way to consolidate password management without having to rely on a master password. It uses AES-256 encryption and supports authorizing and deauthorizing multiple devices for each user.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/bfc63/hallpass.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 35.52492046659597%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Hallpass\"\n        title=\"Hallpass\"\n        src=\"/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/799d3/hallpass.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/00d96/hallpass.png 148w,\n/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/0b23c/hallpass.png 295w,\n/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/799d3/hallpass.png 590w,\n/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/2a3d6/hallpass.png 885w,\n/static/e6904d28f960cb7330a8b513e0909a58/bfc63/hallpass.png 943w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>Stack</h2>\n<h3>Backend</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/about/\">Node.js</a> in combination with <a href=\"https://socket.io/\">socket.io</a> was used to build the api and support push/pull connections.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mongodb.com/\">MongoDB</a> was used for efficient data retrieval</p>\n<h3>Frontend</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://kotlinlang.org/\">Kotlin</a> was used to develop the native Android app\n<a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/swift/\">Swift</a> was used to develop the native iOS app</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Hallpass","date":"January 07, 2017"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/Hallpass/","previous":null,"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/tacky/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Tacky"}}}}}